Core Directory Structure:
lumesquare/
│
├── .github/                  # GitHub workflows and templates
│
├── apps/                     # Monorepo structure for applications
│   ├── backend/              # Backend application
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── api/          # API endpoints, controllers, routes, middleware
│   │   │   ├── blockchain/   # Blockchain integration services
│   │   │   ├── config/       # Application configuration
│   │   │   ├── db/           # Database entities, migrations, repositories
│   │   │   ├── services/     # Business logic by domain
│   │   │   ├── types/        # TypeScript type definitions
│   │   │   ├── utils/        # Utility functions
│   │   │   ├── app.ts        # Express app setup
│   │   │   └── index.ts      # Application entry point
│   │   ├── test/             # Backend tests
│   │   └── scripts/          # Utility scripts
│   │
│   ├── frontend/             # Frontend application
│   │   ├── public/           # Static assets
│   │   ├── src/
│   │   │   ├── components/   # UI components
│   │   │   ├── pages/        # Page components
│   │   │   ├── hooks/        # Custom React hooks
│   │   │   ├── services/     # API integration
│   │   │   ├── store/        # State management
│   │   │   ├── utils/        # Utility functions
│   │   │   └── styles/       # Global styles
│   │   └── test/             # Frontend tests
│   │
│   ├── blockchain/           # Smart contract code
│   │   ├── programs/         # Solana programs (escrow, listings, reputation)
│   │   ├── app/              # Client library for contracts
│   │   ├── tests/            # Contract tests
│   │   └── scripts/          # Deployment & interaction scripts
│   │
│   └── sdk/                  # Rust SDK for P2P marketplaces
│       ├── src/              # SDK source code
│       │   ├── reputation/   # On-chain reputation module
│       │   ├── escrow/       # Escrow management module
│       │   ├── stablecoin/   # Stablecoin integration (Circle)
│       │   ├── solana_pay/   # Solana Pay QR code module
│       │   ├── dispute/      # Dispute resolution module
│       │   ├── sidetrack/    # Sidetrack integration module
│       │   └── lib.rs        # SDK entry point
│       ├── examples/         # Example applications
│       └── tests/            # SDK tests
│
├── infrastructure/           # Infrastructure configuration
│   ├── terraform/            # Infrastructure as code
│   ├── docker/               # Docker configurations
│   └── k8s/                  # Kubernetes manifests
│
├── tools/                    # Development tools
│   ├── load-testing/         # Performance testing
│   ├── security/             # Security tools
│   └── database/             # Database tools
│
├── docs/                     # Documentation
│   ├── api/                  # API documentation
│   ├── architecture/         # Architecture diagrams
│   ├── blockchain/           # Blockchain documentation
│   ├── sdk/                  # SDK documentation
│   └── guides/               # Usage guides
│
└── [config files]            # Root config files (.gitignore, package.json, etc.)

core Backend Structure (apps/backend/src/)
api/: All API-related code (controllers, routes, middlewares)
blockchain/: Smart contract interaction services
db/: Database connectivity, entities, repositories
services/: Core business logic organized by domain
config/: Environment and application configuration

Core SDK Structure (apps/sdk/)
src/: SDK modules and core functionality
reputation/: On-chain reputation verification
escrow/: Escrow management functionality
stablecoin/: Circle SDK integration
solana_pay/: QR code generation and payment processing
dispute/: Dispute resolution system
sidetrack/: Performance optimization integration

Core Smart Contract Structure (apps/blockchain/)
programs/: Contains Solana programs for:
Escrow management
Marketplace listings
User reputation system
tests/: Contract testing
scripts/: Deployment scripts

Core Frontend Structure (apps/frontend/src/)
components/: Reusable UI components
pages/: Page-level components
services/: API integration layer
store/: State management
hooks/: Custom React hooks
